'''国际联盟妇女大会'''（{{lang-en|Inter-Allied Women's Conference}}）于1919年2月10日在巴黎召开，又称'''盟国与美国妇女参政权大会'''（{{lang|en|Suffragist Conference of the Allied Countries and the United States}}{{#tag:ref|部分文献的会议名称是“{{lang|en|Suffragist Conference of the Allied Countries and the United States (US)}}”<ref>{{cite journal | last = Finch | first = George A. | title = The Peace Conference of Paris, 1919 | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-international-law_1919-04_13_2/page/186 | journal = American Journal of International Law | date = 1919-04 | volume = 13 | issue = 2 | page = 186 | doi = 10.2307/2188076 | publisher = American Society of International Law | location = Washington, D.C. | issn = 0002-9300 | jstor = 2188076}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Official Report | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/32026138/official-report-the-guardian-london/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 1919-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190607010706/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/32026138/official_report_the_guardian_london/ | location = London | archive-date = 2019-06-07 | dead-url = no | page = 9 | via = Newspapers.com }}</ref>。|group="注"}}），是[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]结束后与[[巴黎和会_(1919年)|巴黎和会]]同期举行，旨在把妇女问题带入和平进程的国际会议。多次要求参加正式会议遭拒后，国际[[女性參政權|妇女参政权]]运动领导人得以向[[國際勞工組織|国际劳工立法委员会]]表达诉求。4月10日，妇女代表获许向[[國際聯盟|國際聯盟]]委员会提出决议，内容涉及妇女与儿童[[人口贩卖|贩运]]、政治和参政地位、开展教育改革纳入所有国家人民的人权。

与会妇女代表的大部分目标未能实现，但她们的坚持拉开妇女正式参与国际条约谈判帷幕。她们为女子争得出任国际联盟从工作人员到会议代表在内任何职务的权利，推动通过人道主义劳动条件和制止人口贩卖的规定。妇女得以参与正式和平会议证明她们完全有能力涉身国际决策制订，并将人权事务探讨全球化。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Marguerite_de_Witt-Schlumberger.jpg|thumb]]

[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]影响深远，四大帝国沦落并有众多国家诞生或独立，世界政治、文化、经济和社会气候大变<ref>{{cite book | last = Carruthers | first = Amelia | editor-last = Kreisler | editor-first = Fritz | title = Four Weeks in the Trenches: The War Story of a Violinist | chapter = Introduction to the World War One Centenary Series | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=4ymRDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT5&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | edition = Reprint of 1915 Houghton Mifflin publication with new introductory essays | series = WWI Centenary Series | year = 2015 | publisher = Last Post Press | location = Falls Village, CT | isbn = 978-1-4733-6809-5 | page = 5 | access-date = 2021-03-26}}</ref>。1919年的[[巴黎和会_(1919年)|巴黎和会]]旨在初步确立和平条款，计划由全世界33个国家代表参加，还打算以道德和法律原则为基础建立新国际社会秩序<ref name="Charnovitz-2003">{{cite journal | last = Charnovitz | first = Steve | title = The Emergence of Democratic Participation in Global Governance (Paris, 1919) | journal = [[印第安纳大学摩利尔法学院|Indiana Journal of Global Legal Studies]] | date = Winter 2003 | volume = 10 | issue = 1 | pages = 45–77 | publisher = Indiana University Press | location = Bloomington, Indiana | issn = 1543-0367 | jstor = 10.2979/gls.2003.10.1.45 | doi = 10.2979/gls.2003.10.1.45}}</ref>{{rp|61}}。为达成目标，大会呼吁[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]协助，非政府组织和急于通过大力宣传推动议程的游说团体对此极为关注<ref name="Charnovitz-2003" />{{rp|62}}。

和会组织方原计划根据全体会议要求起草条约，但出于恢复国际社会稳定、保密和加快会议进程考虑又不能召集公共议程。和会于是改由[[大不列颠及爱尔兰联合王国|英国]]、[[法兰西第三共和国|法国]]、[[義大利王國_(1861年－1946年)|意大利]]、日本和美国几个主要大国的总理、首相和外长为首组成最高理事会，<ref name="Slosson-1920">{{cite journal | last = Slosson | first = Preston | title = The Constitution of the Peace Conference | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_political-science-quarterly_1920-09_35_3/page/360 | journal = Political Science Quarterly | date = 1920-09 | volume = 35 | issue = 3 | pages = 360–371 | doi = 10.2307/2142581 | publisher = Academy of Political Science | location = New York City, New York | issn = 0032-3195 | jstor = 2142581 | hdl = 2027/osu.32435014547285}}</ref>{{rp|362–363}}<ref name="Dostaler-2007">{{cite book | last = Dostaler | first = Gilles | title = Keynes and His Battles | page = 141 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=kyxmAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA141&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2007 | publisher = Edward Elgar Publishing | location = Cheltenham | access-date = 2021-03-26 | isbn = 978-1-78100-837-9}}</ref>负责为与会代表商谈条约内容<ref name="Dostaler-2007" /><ref name="Slosson-1920" />{{rp|365}}。外交官、政策等领域专家组成52个独立委员会及其他理事会为各种条约的具体条款制订框架<ref name="Dostaler-2007" />，再向最高理事会推荐。这其中的劳工问题委员会和国际联盟委员会后来同意与妇女代表会晤<ref name="Slosson-1920" />{{rp|367–368}}。<ref name="Charnovitz-2003" />{{rp|67}}<ref name="Sluga-2000">{{cite journal | last = Sluga | first = Glenda | title = Female and National Self‐Determination: A Gender Re‐reading of 'The Apogee of Nationalism' | journal = Nations and Nationalism | year = 2000 | volume = 6 | issn = 1354-5078 | doi = 10.1111/j.1354-5078.2000.00495.x | issue = 4 | pages = 495–521 | url = https://www.academia.edu/586750/Female_and_National_Self_Determination_A_Gender_Re_reading_of_The_Apogee_of_Nationalism | access-date = 2021-03-26 | publisher = Wiley-Blackwell for the Association for the Study of Ethnicity and Nationalism | archive-date = 2019-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190510042839/https://www.academia.edu/586750/Female_and_National_Self_Determination_A_Gender_Re_reading_of_The_Apogee_of_Nationalism | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|508}}

世界各国领袖齐聚巴黎，为起草[[停戰協定|停戰協定]]后的和平条款谈判。[[国际妇女联盟|国际妇女参政联盟]]副主席及辅助组织[[法国妇女参政联盟|法国妇女参政联盟]]（{{lang|fr|Union française pour le suffrage des femmes}}）主席[[玛格丽特·德维特-斯伦贝谢|玛格丽特·德维特-斯伦贝谢]]（{{lang|fr|Marguerite de Witt-Schlumberger}}）1919年1月18日致信美国总统[[伍德罗·威尔逊|伍德罗·威尔逊]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Rupp | first = Leila J. | title = Worlds of Women: The Making of an International Women's Movement | url = https://archive.org/details/worldsofwomenmak0000rupp | access-date = 2021-03-26 | page = [https://archive.org/details/worldsofwomenmak0000rupp/page/211 211] | year = 1997 | publisher = [[普林斯頓大學出版社|Princeton University Press]] | location = Princeton, NJ | isbn = 0-691-01675-5}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Offen | first = Karen | title = Debating the Woman Question in the French Third Republic, 1870–1920 | page = 597 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=eEJBDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA597&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2018 | publisher = [[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] | location = Cambridge | isbn = 978-1-107-18804-4}}</ref>，敦促他为妇女参与条约谈判和政策探讨提供方便<ref name="Siegel-2019">{{cite conference | last = Siegel | first = Mona L. | title = In the Drawing Rooms of Paris: The Inter-Allied Women's Conference of 1919 | date = 2019-01-06 | event = 133rd Annual Meeting of the American Historical Association 3–6 January 2019 | location = Chicago, Illinois}}，节选自{{cite book | last = Siegel | first = Mona L. | title = Peace on Our Terms: The Global Battle for Women's Rights After the First World War | year = 2019 | publisher = [[哥倫比亞大學出版社|Columbia University Press]] | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-231-19510-2}}</ref>{{rp|1–2}}。法国妇女参政活动家对[[战争时期的性暴力|针对妇女的战争罪行]]和妇女政治机构缺乏正式发声渠道充满忧虑<ref name="Ferguson-1919">{{cite news | last = Ferguson | title = French in Demand for Strong Action, pt. 1 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704833/the-fort-wayne-sentinel/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200926030052/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704833/the-fort-wayne-sentinel/ | first = Fred S. | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = The Fort Wayne Sentinel | date = 1919-02-17 | location = Ft. Wayne, Indiana | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2020-09-26 | dead-url = no }}和{{cite news | last = Ferguson | first = Fred S. | title = French in Demand for Strong Action, pt. 2 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421155349/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704865/the_fort_wayne_sentinel/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704865/the-fort-wayne-sentinel/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Fort Wayne Sentinel | date = 1919-02-17 | location = Ft. Wayne, Indiana | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | via = Newspapers.com | page = 5 }}</ref>，于1月25日再度致信威尔逊，强调妇女曾与男子并肩作战，无数女子在战争期间支持男子，巴黎和会理应解决妇女议题。威尔逊承认妇女的参与和牺牲，但不同意让女人正式参与和谈，声称妇女关心的议题超出和会范畴，与会代表无权对各国政府如何管理国内事务指手划脚。<ref>{{cite news | title = Votes for Women No Peace Problem | archive-date = 2020-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818073224/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27701948/the-philadelphia-inquirer/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27701948/the-philadelphia-inquirer/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | newspaper = The Philadelphia Inquirer | date = 1919-01-27 | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania | page = 4 | dead-url = no | via = Newspapers.com }}</ref>

2月1日，以《女子生活》（{{lang|fr|''La Vie Feminine''}}）主编<ref>{{cite news | title = Child Welfare to Be Topic of Experts of Four Countries | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36761833/new-york-tribune/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | date = 1919-04-09 | newspaper = [[纽约论坛报|The New York Tribune]] | location = New York, New York | page = 4 | via = Newspapers.com}}</ref>、法国前内阁部长[[加斯顿·汤姆森|加斯顿·汤姆森]]（{{lang|fr|Gaston Thomson}}）之女[[瓦伦丁·汤姆森|瓦伦丁·汤姆森]]（{{lang|fr|Valentine Thomson}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919">{{cite news | last = Drexel | first = Constance | title = French Prohibit Public Meetings Held for Wilson | page = 2 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005164613/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36762078/chicago_tribune/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36762078/chicago-tribune/ | agency = The Chicago Tribune Foreign News Service | newspaper = The Chicago Tribune | location = Chicago, Illinois | access-date = 2021-03-26 | date = 1919-01-26 | archive-date = 2019-10-05 }}</ref>为首的80名法国女子面见威尔逊<ref name="Drexel-1919" /><ref name="Hansen-1919">{{cite news | last = Hansen | first = Harry | title = Women of World Thank Wilson for Fostering Rights | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36761947/the-oregon-daily-journal/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | agency = The Chicago Daily News | date = 1919-02-02 | newspaper = The Oregon Daily Journal | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005164612/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36761947/the_oregon_daily_journal/ | archive-date = 2019-10-05 | location = Portland, Oregon | page = 33 | via = Newspapers.com }}</ref>，呼吁总统把妇女诉求纳入和会议程；威尔逊的答复与之前类似，妇女公民和政治权利属国内事务<ref name="Hansen-1919" />。2月3至8日，[[伯爾尼國際|劳工和社会主义国际大会]]在瑞士[[伯尔尼|伯尔尼]]召开，匈牙利驻瑞士大使、[[女权主义者协会|匈牙利女权主义者协会]]创始人[[罗西卡·史威默|罗西卡·史威默]]（{{lang|en|Rosika Schwimmer}}）组织特别会议<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Zimmermann | first1 = Susan | last2 = Major | first2 = Borbala | editor1-last = de Haan | editor1-first = Francisca | editor2-last = Daskalova | editor2-first = Krassimira | editor3-last = Loutfi | editor3-first = Anna | title = Biographical Dictionary of Women's Movements and Feminisms: Central, Eastern, and South Eastern Europe: 19th and 20th Centuries | year = 2006 | publisher = [[中欧大学|Central European University Press]] | location = Budapest | isbn = 978-963-7326-39-4 | chapter-url = https://muse.jhu.edu/chapter/766195 | chapter = Schwimmer, Róza (Bédy-Schwimmer, Bédi-Schwimmer, Rózsa, Rosika) (1877–1948) | via = Project MUSE | access-date = 2021-03-26 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/biographicaldict0000unse_u3f7/page/484 484–490] | url = https://archive.org/details/biographicaldict0000unse_u3f7/page/484}}</ref>，邀请[[国际妇女争取和平与自由联盟|国际妇女争取永久和平委员会]]成员参加<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|506–507}}。劳工和社会主义国际大会代表决定支持用民主手段建立[[國際聯盟|國際聯盟]]和妇女参与巴黎和谈<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|506–507}}。

法国妇女参政联盟和[[法国妇女全国委员会|法国妇女全国委员会]]（{{lang|fr|Conseil National des femmes françaises}}）成员有样学样，在德维特-斯伦贝谢带领下邀请国际同仁于2月10日和会召开同期齐聚巴黎<ref name="Guerra-2012">{{cite thesis | last1 = Guerra | first1 = Elda | title = L'Associazionismo internazionale delle donne tra diritti, democrazia, politiche di pace 1888 – 1939 | type = PhD | url = https://dspace.unitus.it/bitstream/2067/2468/1/eguerra_tesid.pdf | publisher = Università degli Studi della Tuscia | access-date = 2021-03-26 | page = 76 | date = 2012-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170428051009/https://dspace.unitus.it/bitstream/2067/2468/1/eguerra_tesid.pdf | format = PDF | archive-date = 2017-04-28 | location = Viterbo | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|2}}。她们向所有[[協約國|協約國]]妇女参政权组织发出参加妇女大会的邀请函，向“正式”大会（指巴黎和会）代表转达她们的观点和诉求；法国女权人士同时致力于说服和会男代表支持妇女参与<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|2}}，坚信只有依靠国际合作与协调才能解决国内社会经济问题<ref name="Cobble-2018">{{cite book | last = Cobble | first = Dorothy Sue | editor-last1 = Boris | editor-first1 = Eileen | editor-last2 = Hoehtker | editor-first2 = Dorothea | editor-last3 = Zimmerman | editor-first3 = Susan | title = Women's ILO: Transnational Networks, Global Labour Standards, and Gender Equity, 1919 to Present | chapter = 1: 'The Other ILO Founders': 1919 and Its Legacies | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dntTDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA29&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | pages = 27–49 | year = 2018 | publisher = Brill Publishers | location = Leiden | access-date = 2021-03-26 | isbn = 978-90-04-36043-3}}</ref>{{rp|29}}。响应号召派代表参加大会或带来所在国情况的国家包括法国、意大利、英国、美国、亚美尼亚、比利时、新西兰、波兰、罗马尼亚、南非<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref name="Oldfield-2003">{{cite book | editor-last = Oldfield | editor-first = Sybil | title = International Woman Suffrage: Ius Suffragii 1913–1920 | volume = IV: October 1918 – September 1920 | access-date = 2021-03-26 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=qvAZ8MIP4VcC&pg=PA104&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | publisher = Taylor & Francis | location = London | isbn = 978-0-415-25740-4 | chapter = France: The Inter-Allied Conference in Paris | year = 2003}}</ref>{{rp|89, 104}}<ref name="Andrews-1919">{{cite report | last = Andrews | first = Fannie Fern | title = Letter to Carrie Chapman Catt | date = 1919-06-20 | location = Boston | via = ASP: Women and Social Movements | page = 2 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190129122755/https://cdn.alexanderstreet.com/dorp/apdf/0/71fd/f619/1003463247.a.pdf?e=1548790711&h=7c4e83f8a9c7a02463ea3e5db00165e7 | archive-date = 2019-01-29 | access-date = 2021-03-26 | url = https://cdn.alexanderstreet.com/dorp/apdf/0/71fd/f619/1003463247.a.pdf?e=1548790711&h=7c4e83f8a9c7a02463ea3e5db00165e7 | dead-url = no }}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref name="The Star Tribune-1919">{{cite news | title = Women Who Plead for International Suffrage | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/31440384/star-tribune/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | newspaper = The Star Tribune | date = 1919-03-16 | location = Minneapolis, Minnesota | page = 10 | via = Newspapers.com}}</ref>。

== 动作 ==
=== 二月 ===
[[File:Millicent_Fawcett.jpg|thumb]]]]

巴黎和会谈判从1919年1月持续到5月<ref name="Charnovitz-2003" />{{rp|60}}，妇女大会从2月中旬持续到4月中旬<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|1}}。2月10日大会开幕，巴黎青年律师协会副主席、法国妇女参政联盟中央委员会书记员、女律师苏珊·格林伯格（{{lang|en|Suzanne Grinberg}}）担任大会书记<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|310}}。汤姆森与法国妇女参政联盟成员<ref>{{cite book | last = Pedersen | first = Jean Elisabeth | editor-last1 = Barton | editor-first1 = Nimisha | editor-last2 = Hopkins | editor-first2 = Richard S. | title = Practiced Citizenship: Women, Gender, and the State in Modern France | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=9wt-DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA137&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2019 | publisher = University of Nebraska Press | location = Lincoln | isbn = 978-1-4962-1247-4 | chapter = Women's Activist Social Novels and the French Search for Social Reform, 1880–1914 | pages = 137, 147 | access-date = 2021-03-26}}</ref><ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}、作家[[路易丝·康潘|路易丝·康潘]]（{{lang|fr|Louise Compain}}）充当格林伯格的编辑和翻译<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}。德裔美国报社记者[[康斯坦斯·德雷克塞尔|康斯坦斯·德雷克塞尔]]（{{lang|en|Constance Drexel}}）在大会期间与妇女代表合作，为[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥论坛报外国通讯社]]撰写每日报导<ref name="The Chicago Tribune-1919">{{cite news | title = They Got Equality for Women in the League of Nations | url = https://chicagotribune.newspapers.com/clip/36796190/chicago-tribune/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191006060913/https://chicagotribune.newspapers.com/clip/36796190/chicago_tribune/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | newspaper = The Chicago Tribune | date = 1919-04-29 | location = Chicago, Illinois | page = 5 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-10-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Edwards | first = John Carver | title = Berlin calling: American Broadcasters in Service to the Third Reich | location = New York | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=SyJnAAAAMAAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | year = 1991 | publisher = [[格林伍德出版集團|Praeger Publishing]] | page = 16 | isbn = 978-0-275-93905-2 | access-date = 2021-03-26}}</ref>。

2月11日<ref name="Drexel-1919b">{{cite news | last = Drexel | first = Constance | title = Suffragists in Paris Pleased at Wilson Visit | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36778744/chicago-tribune/ | agency = The Chicago Tribune Foreign News Service | newspaper = The Chicago Tribune | location = Chicago, Illinois | access-date = 2021-03-26 | date = 1919-02-12 | page = 2 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-10-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005230218/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36778744/chicago_tribune/ }}</ref>，[[英國的婦女參政權|英国妇女参政运动]]领导人、[[全國婦女選舉權聯盟|全國婦女選舉權聯盟]]主席[[米利琴特·費塞特|米利琴特·費塞特]]<ref>{{cite ODNB | last = Howarth | first = Janet | title = Fawcett, Dame Millicent Garrett [''née'' Millicent Garrett] (1847–1929) | url = https://www.oxforddnb.com/view/10.1093/ref:odnb/9780198614128.001.0001/odnb-9780198614128-e-33096 | doi = 10.1093/ref:odnb/33096 | date = 2007-10-04 | access-date = 2021-03-27}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>为首的代表团拜访威尔逊<ref name="Sluga-2006">{{cite book | last = Sluga | first = Glenda | title = The Nation, Psychology, and International Politics, 1870–1919 | year = 2006 | publisher = Palgrave Macmillan | location = London | isbn = 978-1-349-28309-5 | pages = 106–131 | chapter = 5. Gender and the Apogee of Nationalism, 1914–1919 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5FCEDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA108&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | access-date = 2021-03-27}}</ref><ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|4}}。其他成员包括亚美尼亚代表[[泽贝尔·耶赛恩|泽贝尔·耶赛恩]]（{{lang|en|Zabel Yesayan}}）<ref name="The Guardian-1919">{{cite news | title = Women and the Peace Conference | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13469815/women-and-the-peace-conference-the/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 1919-02-18 | location = London | via = Newspapers.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308103226/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13469815/women-and-the-peace-conference-the/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | page = 5 }}</ref><ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}，她带来报告反映战争期间亚美尼亚和马其顿妇女被掳并关进[[後宮_(伊斯蘭)|后宫]]的问题<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|105}}。意大利全国赞成选举权联合会主席[[玛格丽塔·安科纳|玛格丽塔·安科纳]]（{{lang|it|Margherita Ancona}}）<ref name="Guerra-2012" /><ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}；[[妇女自由联盟|妇女自由联盟]]成员兼新闻工作者<ref>{{cite news | title = Women's Suffrage | page = 14 | via = Newspapers.com | location = London | newspaper = The Guardian | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36775393/womens-suffrage-the-guardian/ | access-date = 2021-03-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005205653/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36775393/womens_suffrage_the_guardian/ | archive-date = 2019-10-05 | date = 1912-06-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、南非联盟成员[[妮娜·博伊尔|妮娜·博伊尔]]（{{lang|en|Nina Boyle}}）<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref name="The Guardian-1919" />。比利时代表包括该国妇女参政权联合会主席简·布里戈德（{{lang|en|Jane Brigode}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|69}}、比利时全国妇女理事会和妇女权利联盟主席[[玛丽·帕伦特|玛丽·帕伦特]]（{{lang|en|Marie Parent}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919b" />。英国代表包括全國婦女選舉權聯盟成员[[雷·斯特雷奇|雷·斯特雷奇]]（{{lang|en|Ray Strachey}}<ref>{{cite web | last = Willis | first = Angela | title = The Suffragist Caravanners | url = https://nationalmotormuseum.org.uk/the-suffragette-caravanners/ | website = The National Motor Museum | publisher = The National Motor Museum Trust | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200928012853/https://nationalmotormuseum.org.uk/the-suffragette-caravanners/ | archive-date = 2020-09-28 | location = Beaulieu, Hampshire | year = 2018 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Drexel-1919b" />，另一位是罗莎蒙德·史密斯（{{lang|en|Rosamond Smith}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919b" />。法国代表除德维特-斯伦贝谢外<ref name="Drexel-1919c">{{cite news | last = Drexel | first = Constance | title = Women's Conference in Paris | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005230216/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36778978/chicago_tribune/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36778978/chicago-tribune/ | agency = The Chicago Tribune Foreign News Service | newspaper = The Chicago Tribune | location = Chicago, Illinois | access-date = 2021-03-27 | date = 1919-02-13 | page = 8 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-10-05 }}</ref>，还有法国妇女参政联盟创始人兼首任秘书长[[塞西尔·布伦施维格|塞西尔·布伦施维格]]（{{lang|fr|Cécile Brunschvicg}}）<ref>{{cite web | last = Caron | first = Vicki | title = Cécile Brunschvicg | url = https://jwa.org/encyclopedia/article/brunschvicg-cecile | website = Jewish Women's Archive | publisher = Jewish Women: A Comprehensive Historical Encyclopedia | date = 2009-02-27 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200750/http://jwa.org/encyclopedia/article/brunschvicg-cecile | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | location = Brookline, Massachusetts | access-date = 2021-03-27 }}</ref>，法国妇女全国委员会立法机构主席[[玛格丽特·皮雄-兰德里|玛格丽特·皮雄-兰德里]]（{{lang|fr|Marguerite Pichon-Landry}}）<ref>{{cite web | last = Bard | first = Christine | title = Marguerite Pichon-Landry (1878–1972) | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | year = 2015 | url = http://musea.univ-angers.fr/rubriques/elements/popup/popup_esp.php?ref_notice=679 | website = musea.univ-angers.fr | publisher = [[昂热大学|University of Angers]] | location = Angers | access-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191433/http://musea.univ-angers.fr/rubriques/elements/popup/popup_esp.php?ref_notice=679 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="Drexel-1919c" />。美国代表有联邦政府妇女社会卫生部长[[凯瑟琳·贝曼·戴维斯|凯瑟琳·贝曼·戴维斯]]（{{lang|en|Katharine Bement Davis}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919b" /><ref>{{cite news | title = French Women See American Moving Pictures | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191006042024/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36794208/greenville_news/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36794208/greenville-news/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | date = 1919-01-25 | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Greenville Daily News | location = Greenville, North Carolina | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-10-06 }}</ref>，[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]妇女委员会主席[[弗洛伦斯·贾弗里·哈里曼|弗洛伦斯·贾弗里·哈里曼]]（{{lang|en|Florence Jaffray Harriman}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919b" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Women as a Factor in the Political Campaign | page = 44 | via = Newspapers.com | date = 1912-09-08 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36748234/daily-arkansas-gazette/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = The Daily Arkansas Gazette | location = Little Rock, Arkansas | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210810214239/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36748234/daily-arkansas-gazette/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[全国节育联盟|全国节育联盟]]和[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]][[科尼什_(新罕布什尔州)|科尼什]]（{{lang|en|Cornish}}）平等参政权联盟成员[[朱丽叶·巴雷特·鲁比|朱丽叶·巴雷特·鲁比]]（{{lang|en|Juliet Barrett Rublee}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919b" /><ref>{{cite book | last = Johnson | first = Joan Marie | title = Funding Feminism: Monied Women, Philanthropy, and the Women's Movement, 1870–1967 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 183 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5KIvDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA183&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | year = 2017 | publisher = University of North Carolina Press | location = Chapel Hill | isbn = 978-1-4696-3470-8}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Suffragists to Ask Conference Delegates to Back Resolution | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704490/new-york-tribune/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = [[纽约论坛报|The New York Tribune]] | date = 1919-02-12 | location = New York, New York | page = 2 | via = Newspapers.com}}</ref>。代表团提议和会增设妇女委员会关注妇女和儿童议题<ref name="Sluga-2006" /><ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|4}}，威尔逊在会上提议由巴黎和会男外交官组建妇女委员会，国际联盟妇女大会充当顾问机构<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|4}}。

2月12日<ref>{{cite news | last = Drexel | first = Constance | title = Women Adopt Peace Code | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36767343/chicago-tribune/ | agency = The Chicago Tribune Foreign News Service | newspaper = The San Antonio Evening News | location = San Antonio, Texas | access-date = 2021-03-27 | date = 1919-02-15 | page = 3 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210810212837/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36767343/chicago-tribune/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，妇女大会代表团前往[[爱丽舍宫|爱丽舍宫]]拜访[[法国总统|法国总统]][[雷蒙·普恩加萊|雷蒙·普恩加萊]]和夫人[[亨丽埃特·普恩加莱|亨丽埃特]]（{{lang|fr|Henriette Poincaré}}）。代表团成员包括德维特-斯伦贝谢<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}、[[妇女基督教禁酒联盟|妇女基督教禁酒联盟]]新西兰[[尼爾遜|尼爾遜]]分会主席[[露丝·阿特金森|露丝·阿特金森]]（{{lang|en|Ruth Atkinson}}）<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref>{{cite news | title = Women and Peace | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = The Auckland Star | volume = L | issue = 93 | date = 1919-04-19 | url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19190419.2.114.2?query=Ruth+Atkinson&items_per_page=10&start_date=01-02-1919&end_date=30-04-1919&snippet=true | location = Auckland | page = 16 | via = [[新西兰国家图书馆|Papers Past]] | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210810212751/https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19190419.2.114.2?query=Ruth+Atkinson&items_per_page=10&start_date=01-02-1919&end_date=30-04-1919&snippet=true | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = W.C.T.U. Convention | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 2 | url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/TC19190430.2.12?query=Ruth+Atkinson&items_per_page=10&start_date=01-02-1919&end_date=30-04-1919&snippet=true | newspaper = The Colonist | volume = LXI | issue = 15059 | date = 1919-04-30 | location = Nelson | via = [[新西兰国家图书馆|Papers Past]] | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210810212742/https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/TC19190430.2.12?query=Ruth+Atkinson&items_per_page=10&start_date=01-02-1919&end_date=30-04-1919&snippet=true | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其他成员来自比利时、法国、意大利、英国，可能还有澳大利亚的代表<ref name="Drexel-1919e">{{cite news | last = Drexel | first = Constance | title = Poincare Gives Women Hope of 'Place in Sun' | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36767343/chicago-tribune/ | agency = The Chicago Tribune Foreign News Service | newspaper = The Chicago Tribune | location = Chicago, Illinois | access-date = 2021-03-27 | date = 1919-02-16 | page = 3 | via = Newspapers.com | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005194855/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36767343/chicago_tribune/ | archive-date = 2019-10-05 }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|代表团可能没有来自澳大利亚的代表，1919年1至5月澳大利亚报纸只报导新西兰人士阿特金森与会，没有提到澳大利亚代表<ref>{{cite news | title = Women and Children | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36771024/the-sydney-morning-herald/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = [[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 1919-02-17 | location = Sydney, New South Wales | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191005194858/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36771024/the_sydney_morning_herald/ | archive-date = 2019-10-05 | dead-url = no | page = 7 | via = Newspapers.com }}</ref>；历史学家[[蒙娜·西格尔|蒙娜·西格尔]]（{{lang|en|Mona L. Siegel}}）与[[格伦达·斯卢加|格伦达·斯卢加]]（{{lang|en|Glenda Sluga}}）的研究著作都没有提及澳大利亚代表与会<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|498}}。|group="注"}}。此外还有三名美国代表：哈里曼、鲁比，以及[[基督教青年会|基督教青年会]]法国分会主席[[哈丽特·泰勒|哈丽特·泰勒]]（{{lang|en|Harriet Taylor}}）<ref name="Drexel-1919e" />。2月13日，威尔逊将妇女大会请求转达他与[[阿瑟·貝爾福|阿瑟·貝爾福]]（英）、[[乔治·克列孟梭|乔治·克列孟梭]]（法）、[[罗伯特·蓝辛|罗伯特·蓝辛]]（美）、[[牧野伸顯|牧野伸顯]]男爵（[[大日本帝国|日本]]）、[[第一代米尔纳子爵阿尔弗雷德·米尔纳|阿尔弗雷德·米尔纳]]（{{lang|en|Alfred Milner}}，英）、[[维托里奥·埃曼努尔·奥兰多|维托里奥·埃曼努尔·奥兰多]]（意）、[[斯蒂芬·皮雄|斯蒂芬·皮雄]]（{{lang|fr|Stephen Pichon}}，法）、[[西德尼·桑尼诺|西德尼·桑尼诺]]（{{lang|it|Sidney Sonnino}}，意）等人构成的十人理事会，以及[[甘加_·_辛格|甘加 · 辛格]]（{{lang|en|Ganga Singh}}，[[英属印度|印]]）和其他政要<ref name="Sluga-2006" /><ref name="Minutes of Meetings-1919">{{cite report | title = The Council of Ten: Minutes of Meetings January 12 to February 14, 1919 | url = http://images.library.wisc.edu/FRUS/EFacs/1919Parisv03/reference/frus.frus1919parisv03.i0008.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923105059/http://images.library.wisc.edu/FRUS/EFacs/1919Parisv03/reference/frus.frus1919parisv03.i0008.pdf | access-date = 2021-03-27 | publisher = United States Department of State | pages = 1013–1038 | year = 1919 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | location = Washington, DC | date =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但他们还是没有接受妇女大会诉求<ref name="Sluga-2006" />。法国总理克列孟梭建议妇女大会与劳工委员会合作<ref name="Charnovitz-2003" />{{rp|67}}{{#tag:ref|2月13日巴黎和会正式会议记录没有记载妇女大会提议讨论<ref name="Minutes of Meetings-1919" />，[[悉尼大學|悉尼大學]]历史学家格伦达·斯卢加声称“美国和谈委员会”的档案记录包含此次“秘密会议”内容<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|498}}。|group="注"}}。

连连碰壁的妇女大会没有灰心，继续争取和会代表支持。[[朱尔斯·康本|朱尔斯·康本]]（{{lang|en|Jules Cambon}}）、[[保罗·海曼斯|保罗·海曼斯]]（{{lang|en|Paul Hymans}}）和普恩加莱都在会晤后表示，对亚美尼亚、比利时、[[希臘王國|希腊]]、法国、波兰和[[南斯拉夫王國|塞尔维亚]]驱逐妇女，以及希腊与[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]贩卖妇女这类重大问题应当听取妇女意见，妇女大会可以提供重要参考。<ref name="Ferguson-1919" />部分从英国赶来的女士二月底回国，全国妇女选举权联盟执行委员会委员[[玛格丽·科贝特·阿什比|玛格丽·科贝特·阿什比]]（{{lang|en|Margery Corbett Ashby}}）<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Law | first = Cheryl | title = Women: A Modern Political Dictionary | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=iTnXdlutlVsC&pg=PA45&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | year = 2000 | publisher = I.B. Tauris | location = London | isbn = 978-1-86064-502-0 | chapter = Corbett-Ashby, Margery Irene | pages = [https://archive.org/details/womenmodernpolit0000lawc/page/45 45–46] | access-date = 2021-03-27 | url = https://archive.org/details/womenmodernpolit0000lawc/page/45}}</ref>，倡导刑事改革的前[[英国全国妇女理事会|全国女工联盟]]主席、妇女选举权宪法协会成员[[玛格丽·弗莱|玛格丽·弗莱]]（{{lang|en|Margery Fry}}）在三月初赶到<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}<ref>{{cite journal | last = Logan | first = Anne | title = Political Life in the Shadows: The Post Suffrage Political Career of S. Margery Fry (1874–1958) | doi = 10.1080/09612025.2013.820605 | date = 2014-01-17 | volume = 23 | issue = 3 | journal = Women's History Review | publisher = Taylor and Francis | location = Abingdon, Oxfordshire | issn = 0961-2025 | page = 371}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Morton | first = Tara | title = Suffrage Societies Database Guide | access-date = 2021-03-27 | year = 2018 | archive-date = 2020-12-02 | url = https://www.suffrageresources.org.uk/resource/3231/suffrage-societies-database-guide | website = Suffrage Resources | publisher = Historical Association and the Association for Citizenship Teaching | location = London | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201202094142/https://www.suffrageresources.org.uk/resource/3231/suffrage-societies-database-guide | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，[[米蘭|米蘭]]意大利全国妇女联盟的[[格拉齐耶拉·桑尼诺|格拉齐耶拉·桑尼诺·卡尔皮]]（{{lang|it|Graziella Sonnino Carpi}}）<ref name="The Star Tribune-1919" /><ref>{{cite thesis | last = Hornbach | first = Katja Gerhartzaus | title = Le madri della Patria: Bürgerliche Frauenbewegung, Nationalismus und Krieg in Italien (1900–1922) | archive-date = 2019-10-06 | page = 204 | format = PDF | dead-url = no | url = https://docserv.uni-duesseldorf.de/servlets/DerivateServlet/Derivate-2814/814.pdf | type = PhD | year = 2003 | publisher = [[杜塞尔多夫大学|Heinrich Heine University Düsseldorf]] | location = Düsseldorf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191006065742/https://docserv.uni-duesseldorf.de/servlets/DerivateServlet/Derivate-2814/814.pdf | access-date = 2021-03-27 }}</ref>，波兰的伊娃·米特奇玛（{{lang|en|Eva Mitzhouma}}）均在二月底赶来巴黎参加妇女大会<ref name="The Star Tribune-1919" />。

=== 三月 ===
妇女大会代表与16个国家的巴黎和会代表会晤争取支持，希望至少能让妇女代表加入可能处理妇女儿童议题的委员会<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|6}}。3月11日，以德维特-斯伦贝谢为首的妇女代表团同十人理事会面谈，但威尔逊没有参与<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|508}}<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|7}}。在场和会代表同意妇女代表旁听[[國際勞工組織|国际劳工立法委员会]]和国际联盟委员会磋商<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|508}}。虽然这还远远没有达到妇女代表期望，但妇女正式参与国际条约谈判已是史无前例<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|7}}。

3月18日，提倡妇女参政权的证人向国际劳工立法委员会作证，概述妇女工作条件<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|508}}<ref name="Charnovitz-2003" />{{rp|68}}<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}。这些证人除英国代表阿什比外，还有法国代表布伦施维格<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}，女裁缝兼[[法国基督教工人联合会|法国基督教工人联合会]]（{{lang|fr|Confédération française des travailleurs chrétiens}}）成员尤金·贝克曼斯（{{lang|fr|Eugénie Beeckmans}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Chabot | first = Joceline | title = Les débuts du syndicalisme féminin chrétien en France, 1899–1944 | page = 30 | isbn = 978-2-7297-0730-9 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=_I-I4RCLRvcC&pg=PA30&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2003 | publisher = Presses Universitaires Lyon | location = Lyon | access-date = 2021-03-27}}</ref>、[[總工會_(法國)|法国总工会]]工人代表乔其纱·布约特（{{lang|fr|Georgette Bouillot}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref name="Cobble-2018" />{{rp|30}}、法国在家工作办事处（{{lang|fr|Office français du travail à domicile}}）创始人、工会成员[[珍妮·布维耶|珍妮·布维耶]]（{{lang|fr|Jeanne Bouvier}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref name="Cobble-2018" />{{rp|30}}；同为法国在家工作办事处创始人的[[和平主義|和平主义者]]、法国妇女全国委员会成员[[加布里埃尔·杜尚|加布里埃尔·杜尚]]（{{lang|fr|Gabrielle Duchêne}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref name="Cobble-2018" />{{rp|30}}<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Dreyfus | first1 = Michel | last2 = Racine | first2 = Nicole | title = Duchêne Gabrielle (Duchêne Mathilde, Denise, dite) | dead-url = no | url = https://maitron.fr/?article23137&id_mot=5457 | website = Maitron | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024330/http://maitron-en-ligne.univ-paris1.fr/spip.php?article23137&id_mot=5457 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | location = Paris | date = 2008-10-25 }}</ref>；律师、新闻工作者兼[[法国妇女权利联盟|法国妇女权利联盟]]（{{lang|fr|Ligue française pour le droit des femmes}}）秘书长[[玛丽亚·维罗纳|玛丽亚·维罗纳]]（{{lang|fr|Maria Vérone}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Kimble | first = Sara L. | editor-last1 = Kimble | editor-first1 = Sara L. | editor-last2 = Röwekamp  | editor-first2 = Marion | title = New Perspectives on European Women's Legal History | chapter = The rise of "Modern Portias": Feminist Legal Activism in Republican France, 1890s–1940s | year = 2016 | publisher = Routledge | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-317-57716-4 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=vkuTDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA139&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 139}}</ref>。其他国家代表包括哈里曼（美）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}、巴黎和会意大利代表马里亚诺·达梅里奥（{{lang|it|Mariano D'Amelio}}）的夫人玛丽·达梅里奥-蒂沃利（{{lang|it|Marie d'Amalio-Tivoli}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref name="Clemente-1986">{{cite web | last = Clemente | first = Vincenzo | title = D'Amelio, Mariano | year = 1986 | url = https://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/mariano-d-amelio_(Dizionario-Biografico) | website = [[意大利百科全书|Treccani]] | publisher = Dizionario Biografico degli Italiani, Volume 32 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200106002016/http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/mariano-d-amelio_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ | archive-date = 2020-01-06 | location = Rome }}</ref><ref name="Naldi-2010">{{cite book | last = Naldi | first = Nerio | editor-last1 = Vint | editor-first1 = John | editor-last2 = Metcalfe | editor-first2 = J. Stanley | editor-last3 = Kurz | editor-first3 = Heinz D. | editor-last4 = Salvadori | editor-first4 = Neri | editor-last5 = Samuelson | editor-first5 = Paul | title = Economic Theory and Economic Thought: Essays in Honour of Ian Steedman | page = 260 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=27yLAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA260&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2010 | publisher = Routledge | location = London | isbn = 978-1-135-18300-4 | chapter = 17. Piero Sraffa in his Family: 1898 to 1916 | access-date = 2021-03-27}}</ref>{{#tag:ref|不同文献记载的玛丽·达梅里奥-蒂沃利原名有差异。[[范妮·弗恩·安德鲁斯|范妮·弗恩·安德鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Fannie Fern Andrews}}）写给[[凯莉·查普曼·卡特|凯莉·查普曼·卡特]]（{{lang|en|Carrie Chapman Catt}}）的信所记是“{{lang|en|Madame D'Amatio Tivoli, Italy}}”（达梅里奥·蒂沃利夫人，意大利），不能肯定“蒂沃利”到底是[[蒂沃利|意大利地名]]还是达梅里奥夫人的姓氏<ref name="Andrews-1919" />。西比尔·奥德菲尔德（{{lang|en|Sybil Oldfield}}）认为是姓氏<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89, 104}}，《芝加哥论坛报》所列人名是“{{lang|en|Mme. d'Amalio-Tivoli}}”（达梅里奥-蒂沃利女士）<ref name="The Chicago Tribune-1919" />，其他文献认可《芝加哥论坛报》的记载。<ref name="Clemente-1986" /><ref name="Naldi-2010" />|group="注"}}，以及比利时基督教女权主义（{{lang|fr|Féminisme chrétien de Belgique}}）创始人[[路易丝·范登普拉斯|路易丝·范登普拉斯]]（{{lang|fr|Louise van den Plas}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}<ref>{{cite journal | last = Gérin | first = Paul | title = Louise Van den Plas et les débuts du "Feminisme Chrétien de Belgique" | journal = Belgisch Tijdschrift voor Nieuwste Geschiedenis | year = 1969 | volume = 1 | issue = 2 | page = 260 | archive-date = 2020-08-02 | issn = 0035-0869 | format = PDF | dead-url = no | url = https://www.journalbelgianhistory.be/nl/system/files/article_pdf/BTNG-RBHC%2C%2001%2C%201969%2C%202%2C%20pp%20254-275.pdf | access-date = 2021-03-27 | publisher = Centre for Historical Research and Documentation on War and Contemporary Society | location = Brussels | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200802081448/https://www.journalbelgianhistory.be/nl/system/files/article_pdf/BTNG-RBHC%2C%2001%2C%201969%2C%202%2C%20pp%20254-275.pdf }}</ref>。

妇女大会代表向国际劳工立法委员会主席[[龔帕斯|龔帕斯]]递交决议，涵盖工作条件对健康的危害等多种议题。她们建议限制每天和每周工作时间，分析生活成本制订合理的最低工资标准，同工同酬；呼吁规管[[童工|童工]]、[[產假與育嬰假|带薪产假]]和[[职业教育|技术职业培训]]。她们还要求各国建立正式妇女成员组织，这些组织有权分析可能影响妇女的立法政策并提出建议。<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|89}}美国工会成员[[玛丽·安德森|玛丽·安德森]]（{{lang|en|Mary Anderson}}）和[[罗斯·施耐德曼|罗斯·施耐德曼]]（{{lang|en|Rose Schneiderman}}）抵达巴黎的时间太晚，没赶上向国际劳工立法委员会作证，她们与威尔逊会晤，呼吁让妇女融入全球治理框架，总统承诺做到但没有落实<ref name="Cobble-2018" />{{rp|31–32}}。妇女代表到三月底已促使和会代表同意妇女可从事国际联盟所有职务，[[第一代切爾伍德的塞西爾子爵羅伯特·塞西爾|罗伯特·塞西尔勋爵]]递交决议，国际联盟委员会3月28日投票一致通过<ref>{{cite news | title = 3 Amendments to League Held Over by Envoys | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704684/the-st-louis-star-and-times/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | newspaper = The St. Louis Star | date = 1919-03-28 | location = St. Louis, Missouri | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421135854/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/27704684/the_st_louis_star_and_times/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 四月 ===
[[File:Lady_Ishbel_Aberdeen_1899_IIAV_15541_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]

妇女代表与国际劳工立法委员会磋商后，[[国际妇女理事会|国际妇女理事会]]主席[[阿伯丁和特麦尔侯爵夫人伊什贝尔·汉密尔顿-戈登|阿伯丁夫人]]（{{lang|en|Lady Aberdeen}}）抵达巴黎，协助筹备向国际联盟委员会介绍妇女诉求。她召集众多妇女代表准备向和会代表宣读的决议，其中主要关注三大领域：公民地位、政治地位、人权。<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104–105}}她们宣称国际法没有明确妇女和儿童的公民地位，对容忍[[童婚|童婚]]、[[性交易|卖淫]]和妇女儿童[[人口贩卖|贩运]]宽大处理，将妇女视为丈夫和父亲[[動產|动产]]的民法规定深表忧虑，呼吁从国际法层面提供保护<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|105}}，还建议设立公共健康保护机构，就卫生和疾病问题向公众提供建议。决议指出，妇女在战争期间受苦受难，同时军人走上前线导致后方空虚，许多工作都是妇女完成，为祖国安全和福祉贡献很大。她们要求赋予女人参政权，为她们参与政府治理打开大门。决议最后呼吁在国际高度确保基础教育提供文明与公民义务培训，强调尊重所有国家公民的人文、文化和[[人权|人权]]。<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|106}}
[[File:Inter-Allied_Women's_Conference_end.png|thumb]]

4月10日，国际联盟妇女大会17名代表向国际联盟委员会提出诉求<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|7}}，其中包括阿伯丁夫人、德维特-斯伦贝谢、阿什比、布伦施维格、弗莱、格林伯格、鲁比、达梅里奥-蒂沃利、维罗纳。其他法国代表包括法国妇女参政联盟和国际妇女理事会指导委员会成员[[加布里埃尔·阿尔芬·萨尔瓦多|加布里埃尔·阿尔芬·萨尔瓦多]]，（{{lang|fr|Gabrielle Alphen-Salvador}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite web | last = Bouquet | first = Brigitte | title = Alphen-Salvador Gabrielle (1856–1920) | archive-date = 2019-02-04 | dead-url = no | url = http://www.cedias.org/index.php?lvl=cmspage&pageid=4&id_article=257 | website = Cedias – Musée Social | publisher = Social Service History Research Group | location = Paris | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190204021234/http://www.cedias.org/index.php?lvl=cmspage&pageid=4&id_article=257 | year = 2019 }}</ref>军医兼法国妇女参政联盟宣传人士[[妮可·吉拉德-曼金|妮可·吉拉德-曼金]]（{{lang|fr|Nicole Girard-Mangin}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite magazine | last = Morant | first = Guillaume de | title = Nicole Girard-Mangin, première femme médecin sur le front | archive-date = 2020-10-28 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.parismatch.com/Actu/Societe/Nicole-Girard-Mangin-premiere-femme-medecin-sur-le-front-578852 | magazine = Paris Match | location = Paris | access-date = 2021-03-27 | issn = 0397-1635 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201028184512/https://www.parismatch.com/Actu/Societe/Nicole-Girard-Mangin-premiere-femme-medecin-sur-le-front-578852 | date = 2014-08-04 }}</ref>，法国妇女参政联盟书记玛丽-路易丝·普希（{{lang|fr|Marie-Louise Puech}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite web | title = Témoignages de 1914–1918: Puech-Milhau, Marie-Louise (1876–1966) | archive-date = 2019-04-22 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | url = http://www.crid1418.org/temoins/2015/06/13/puech-milhau-marie-louise-1876-1966/ | website = Crid1418 | publisher = Collectif de Recherche International et de Débat sur la Guerre de 1914–1918 | location = Marseilles | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190422194547/http://www.crid1418.org/temoins/2015/06/13/puech-milhau-marie-louise-1876-1966/ | date = 2015-06-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、新闻工作者兼法国妇女全国委员会书记[[艾薇儿·德圣克罗克斯|艾薇儿·德圣克罗克斯]]（{{lang|fr|Avril de Sainte-Croix}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Offen | first1 = Karen | last2 = Bruhat | first2 = Michèle (translator) | title = "La plus grande féministe de France". Mais qui est donc Madame Avril de Sainte-Croix? | journal = Bulletin Archives du Féminisme | issue = 9 | date = 2005-12 | url = https://www.archivesdufeminisme.fr/sommaires-des-bulletins/bulletin-09/offen-k-grande-feministe-france-mme-avril-sainte-croix/ | access-date = 2021-03-27 | publisher = Presses Universitaires de Rennes | location = Rennes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200215183749/https://www.archivesdufeminisme.fr/sommaires-des-bulletins/bulletin-09/offen-k-grande-feministe-france-mme-avril-sainte-croix/ | archive-date = 2020-02-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，法国妇女全国委员会主席[[朱莉·西格弗里德|朱莉·西格弗里德]]（{{lang|en|Julie Siegfried}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Feutry | first = David | title = Rebelles de la foi. Les protestants en France, XVI–XXIe siècle | year = 2017 | publisher = Éditions Belin | isbn = 978-2-410-01167-8 | location = Paris | page = 204 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=EBw3DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT204&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | access-date = 2021-03-27}}</ref>。其他代表包括[[罗马尼亚总理|罗马尼亚总理]][[扬·约内尔·布勒蒂亚努|扬·约内尔·布勒蒂亚努]]的夫人[[埃丽莎·布勒蒂亚努|埃丽莎·布勒蒂亚努]]（{{lang|ro|Elisa Brătianu}}）<ref name="Andrews-1919" /><ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}，加拿大裔美国教师、和平主义者<ref>{{cite news | last = Downing | first = Margaret B. | title = Apostle of Peace to Schools (pt 1) | date = 1913-01-05 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/32793919/apostle-of-peace-to-schools-the-boston/ | newspaper = The Boston Globe | location = Boston, Massachusetts | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 56a | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309181137/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/32793919/apostle-of-peace-to-schools-the-boston/ | dead-url = no }}和{{cite news | last = Downing | first = Margaret B. | title = Apostle of Peace to Schools (pt 2) | date = 1913-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210112053451/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36718251/the-boston-globe/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/36718251/the-boston-globe/ | newspaper = The Boston Globe | location = Boston, Massachusetts | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 56a | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-01-12 }}</ref>、[[妇女和平党|妇女和平党]]成员<ref>{{cite book | title = Year book of the Woman's Peace Party | url = https://archive.org/details/yearbookofwomans1916woma/page/14/mode/2up | year = 1916 | publisher = Women's Peace Party | page = 14 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | location = Chicago, Illinois}}</ref>、美国学校和平联盟创始人[[范妮·弗恩·安德鲁斯|范妮·弗恩·安德鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Fannie Fern Andrews}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite conference | last = Stomfay-Stitz | first = Aline M. | title = Peace Education for Children: Historical Perspectives | page = 7 | url = https://archive.org/details/ERIC_ED381464/page/n8/mode/2up | date = 1994-04-07 | conference = Annual Meeting of the American Educational Research Association | publisher = Education Resources Information Center | access-date = 2021-03-27 | id = ED-381-464}}</ref>，[[意大利妇女全国理事会|意大利妇女全国理事会]]（{{lang|it|Consiglio Nazionale delle Donne Italiane}}）成员爱丽丝·夏沃尼（{{lang|it|Alice Schiavoni}}）<ref name="Oldfield-2003" />{{rp|104}}<ref>{{cite web | last = Bartoloni | first = Stefania | title = Rasponi Spalletti, Gabriella | url = https://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/gabriella-rasponi-spalletti_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ | website = treccani.it | publisher = Biographical Dictionary of Italians – Volume 86 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200127001256/http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/gabriella-rasponi-spalletti_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ | archive-date = 2020-01-27 | year = 2016 | location = Rome | dead-url = no }}</ref>。代表坚持要求妇女在国际联盟所有职位、委员会和机构享有男子同等机遇，不给予妇女平等待遇的政府禁止加入国际联盟<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|7}}。她们主张一旦准许[[民族自決|民族自決]]就应赋予女子生活自主的平等机遇和法律权利。她们要求保障妇女参政权、承诺妇女公民、权利地位和人权的呼声最后沦为空谷足音。不过，纳入《[[凡尔赛条约|凡尔赛条约]]》的《[[国际联盟公约|国际联盟公约]]》第七条承认妇女有权出任国际联盟所有职务。<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|8}}

== 影响 ==
巴黎和会代表拒绝把妇女公民和政治机构视为国际关注议题或人权事务，认为应由各国自行决定公民资格要求，特别是已婚妇女的公民权利<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|500}}。他们认为国际联盟妇女大会在教育、劳工和国籍领域的建议“太过激进”、不能实施，其中大部分未经充分探讨便被拒之门外<ref name="Pietilä-1999">{{cite conference | last = Pietilä | first = Hilkka | title = Engendering the Global Agenda: A Success Story of Women and the United Nations | url = https://ecpr.eu/Filestore/PaperProposal/81ecca4f-4dc8-4050-990c-c861489849f2.pdf | date = 1999-03-31 | conference = European Consortium for Political Research Workshop | format = PDF | conference-url = https://ecpr.eu/Events/PanelList.aspx?EventID=44 | publisher = [[曼海姆大学|University of Mannheim]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308122950/https://ecpr.eu/Filestore/PaperProposal/81ecca4f-4dc8-4050-990c-c861489849f2.pdf | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | location = Mannheim, Baden-Württemberg | access-date = 2021-03-27 | page = 2 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|507}}。不过，《国际联盟公约》包含“成员国应促进男子、女子和儿童人道劳动条件，防止贩卖妇女和儿童”的规定<ref name="Pietilä-1999" />。

大部分支持成立国际联盟的女权人士对《凡尔赛条约》最终条款深感失望。国际妇女争取永久和平委员会1919年5月17至19日在苏黎世举办和会，与会代表谴责《凡尔赛条约》缺乏谴责暴力的规定，同时谴责其中的惩罚措施，批评条约把妇女排除在公民和政治事务之外。<ref>{{cite book | last = Wiltsher | first = Anne | title = Most Dangerous Women: Feminist Peace Campaigners of the Great War | year = 1985 | publisher = Pandora Press | location = London | url = https://archive.org/details/mostdangerouswom00anne_0?view=theater#page/111/mode/1up | pages = 200–202 | isbn = 978-0-86358-010-9 | edition = 1st | access-date = 2021-03-27}}</ref>国际妇女争取永久和平委员会在苏黎世和会更名国际妇女争取和平与自由联盟，与会代表把国际联盟妇女大会的众多构想纳入《妇女宪章》并在会上通过<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|507}}。国际劳工组织初建时属国际联盟机构，该机构将妇女大会提出的同工同酬写入宪章前言<ref name="Cobble-2018" />{{rp|32}}，同时管理文件明确规定国际劳工大会需有女代表参加，大会应讨论妇女议题<ref>{{cite journal | last = Cobble | first = Dorothy Sue | title = Who Speaks for Workers? Japan and the 1919 ILO Debates Over Rights and Global Labor Standards | journal = International Labor and Working-Class History | volume = 87 | date = Spring 2015 | issue = 87 | page = 214 | doi = 10.1017/S0147547914000271 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200102055955/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Who-Speaks-for-Workers-Japan-and-the-1919-ILO-Over-Cobble/41301af4c0c26df45da5b056291528c031d551b3 | archive-date = 2020-01-02 | url = https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Who-Speaks-for-Workers-Japan-and-the-1919-ILO-Over-Cobble/41301af4c0c26df45da5b056291528c031d551b3 | issn = 0147-5479 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

妇女劳工领袖也对谈判结果感到失望，打算参加计划同年11月在哥伦比亚特区召开的国际劳工大会。[[妇女工会联盟|妇女工会联盟]]主席[[玛格丽特·德雷尔·罗宾斯|玛格丽特·德雷尔·罗宾斯]]（{{lang|en|Margaret Dreier Robins}}）认为正式议程肯定又会把妇女排除在外，为此她推动[[1919年国际职业妇女大会|国际职业妇女大会]]在10月29日召开，拟定重要议程准备向国际劳工大会提出。<ref name="Cobble-2014">{{cite journal | last = Cobble | first = Dorothy Sue | title = A Higher "Standard of Life" for the World: U.S. Labor Women's Reform Internationalism and the Legacies of 1919 | journal = The Journal of American History | date = 2014-03 | volume = 100 | issue = 4 | pages = 1052–1085 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200102055945/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/A-Higher-%22Standard-of-Life%22-for-the-World%3A-U.S.-and-Cobble/e73304ef51c0ef9b52f66eff048322ea4a51a21c | doi = 10.1093/jahist/jau005 | url = https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/A-Higher-%22Standard-of-Life%22-for-the-World%3A-U.S.-and-Cobble/e73304ef51c0ef9b52f66eff048322ea4a51a21c | via = Oxford University Press's Oxford Academic | issn = 0021-8723 | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-date = 2020-01-02 | dead-url = no }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>{{rp|1064–1065}}大会代表在十天会议期间把国际联盟妇女大会代表提出的大部分劳工标准和工人权利保障写入决议<ref name="Cobble-2014" />{{rp|1066}}。国际职业妇女大会众多代表随后参加国际劳工大会并积极发言，促使大会对产假、工时和童工问题制订国际劳工标准，不过最后通过的标准依然低于妇女代表提议<ref name="Cobble-2014" />{{rp|1069–1070}}。

== 纪录和研究 ==
第二次世界大战期间，法国、比利时、[[列支敦斯登|列支敦斯登]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]和[[国际妇女运动档案馆|国际妇女运动档案馆]]的女权人士档案遭纳粹洗劫。苏联红军攻入[[納粹德國|納粹德國]]占领区后把这些文献带到莫斯科，存放在[[國家安全委員會_(蘇聯)|国家安全委员会]]的特别档案馆（{{lang|ru|Особый архив}}），后在20世纪90年代初重新发现。受[[開放政策|開放政策]]和[[改革重组|改革重组]]政策改革影响，这些文献最终回到所属国怀抱。<ref name="Poinsotte-2002">{{cite web | last = Poinsotte | first = Valérie | title = Archives Brunschvicg, Cécile (1 AF) | archive-date = 2019-04-22 | date = 2002-06 | url = https://bu.univ-angers.fr/zone/Patrimoine/centre-des-archives-du-feminisme/archives-brunschvicg-cecile-1-af | website = bu.univ-angers.fr | publisher = Bibliothèque Université D'Angers | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190422035024/http://bu.univ-angers.fr/zone/Patrimoine/centre-des-archives-du-feminisme/archives-brunschvicg-cecile-1-af | location = Angers | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = de Haan | first = Francisca | title = Getting to the Source: A "Truly International" Archive for the Women's Movement (IAV, now IIAV): From its Foundation in Amsterdam in 1935 to the Return of its Looted Archives in 2003 | dead-url = yes | url = https://www.atria.nl/earticles/2004/TrulyInternational.pdf | journal = Journal of Women's History | volume = 16 | issue = 4 | pages = 156–161 | publisher = [[約翰斯·霍普金斯大學出版社|Johns Hopkins University Press]] | doi = 10.1353/jowh.2004.0082 | date = Winter 2004 | archive-date = 2018-06-24 | oclc = 71750482 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180624040054/https://atria.nl/earticles/2004/TrulyInternational.pdf | format = PDF | access-date = 2018-06-24 }}</ref>法国档案记录分成两批，在2000年2月和11月交付，再经[[法國外交部|法國外交部]]档案部编目。心血被盗的女权人士早已作古，她们的后裔决定公开档案更有利于后世并创办女权档案馆协会，计划在[[昂热大学|昂热大学]]建立[[女权主义档案馆|女权主义档案馆]]。经过两年整理和分类后档案馆开放，方便学者查阅和评估文献。<ref name="Poinsotte-2002" />

妇女代表与十人理事会及巴黎和会代表的会晤内容没有列入和会正式记录<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|498}}，法国档案又长期遗失<ref name="Poinsotte-2002" />，导致21世纪才有学者开始全面研究国际联盟妇女大会<ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|495}}。新研究结果表明妇女在一战结束之际积极参与和平进程，渴望在国际政策制订过程中承担公共责任。[[澳洲人文學院|澳大利亚人文学院]]历史学家格伦达·斯卢加表示，“女人自决是国家民主化的必然结果”。<ref>{{cite web | title = Author Archives: Glenda Sluga | archive-date = 2021-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117090539/http://humanityjournal.org/author/glenda-sluga/ | dead-url = no | url = http://humanityjournal.org/author/glenda-sluga/ | year = 2016 | website = humanityjournal.org | access-date = 2021-03-27 | publisher = Humanity | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania }}</ref><ref name="Sluga-2000" />{{rp|496–497}}2019年，[[加利福尼亞州立大學|加利福尼亞州立大學]]历史学家蒙娜·西格尔和[[罗格斯大学|罗格斯大学]]历史学家[[多萝西·苏·科布尔|多萝西·苏·科布尔]]（{{lang|en|Dorothy Sue Cobble}}）在第133届[[美國歷史學會|美國歷史學會]]会议演讲，重新评估国际联盟妇女大会对1919年和平进程的意义<ref>{{cite conference | title = Global Feminisms and 1919: Centennial Reconsiderations | url = https://aha.confex.com/aha/2019/webprogram/Session17803.html | date = 2019-01-06 | conference = 133rd Annual Meeting of the American Historical Association 3–6 January 2019, Chicago, Illinois | publisher = [[美國歷史學會|American Historical Association]] | location = Washington, D. C. | access-date = 2021-03-27 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190621171844/https://aha.confex.com/aha/2019/webprogram/Session17803.html | archive-date = 2019-06-21 }}</ref>。西格尔认为与会妇女代表的大部分目标未能实现，但她们的坚持令妇女从此得以正式参与国际条约谈判，促使人权探讨全球化，两项成就影响深远并持续至今<ref name="Siegel-2019" />{{rp|9}}。

